content: Like the 9/11 Commission, the measure establishes a 10-person bipartisan commission with 5 commissioners, including the Chair, appointed by the Speaker & Senate Majority Leader & 5 commissioners, including the Vice Chair, be appointed by the Minority Leaders of the House & Senate
